verbose_text: MMP14 and MMP15 expression was determined by Real-time quantitative PCR (RT-qPCR) using FAM labeled TaqMan gene expression assays (Life Technologies, MMP14 : Hs01037003_g1; MMP15 : Hs00233997_m1), TaqMan universal PCR master mix (Life Technologies) and the CFX96 real-time PCR detection system (BioRad Laboratories, Hercules, CA, USA).
